      "text": "遙子さんは羞恥心を克服するって言ってたけど\n一体どんな特訓をするつもりなのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san said she'll overcome her embarrassment‚\nBut what kind of special training is she planning?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
