      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？\nあれ、遙子さん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!?\nWait‚ Haruko-san!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 20.1
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4676.157633499997,
          "startTime": 25.7761576335
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.3428243001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こんにちは、{user}君が\nこんな朝早く寮にいるなんてめずらしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Hello‚ {user}. It's unusual for you\nto be in the dormitory so early in the morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.3428243001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.8428243001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんの様子が気になって……\nそれより、さっき衣装を着ていませんでしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was worried about how Haruko-san were doing…\nBut more importantly‚ weren't you wearing your outfit earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.4761576335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "着てないわよ？　気のせいじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wasn't wearing it. Maybe it's just your imagination.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4094909668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.3094909668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや着てましたよね、肌を大胆に露出した体のラインが\nはっきり分かる格好でうろうろしてましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ you were definitely wearing it. It was a revealing outfit\nthat clearly showed the lines of your body.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.8094909668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "変質者みたいに言わないでよ、もう！\nでも、確かにそう言われても仕方ないかしら……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't talk like a pervert! Geez!\nBut I guess I can't blame you for saying that…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.1094909668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "実は……あれからみんなに相談してみたの\n羞恥心に打ち勝つにはどうしたらいいかしらって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually… after that‚ I consulted with everyone.\nI asked them how to overcome my embarrassment…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.9428243001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.6428243001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら、こころちゃんが教えてくれたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then Kokoro-chan told me something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6428243001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "「普段から衣装で生活すれば、それが普通になります」\n「恥ずかしくなくなりますよ」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"If you live your daily life in outfits‚ it will become normal.\"\n\"You won't feel embarrassed anymore\" …",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "衣装を着たままコンビニで買い物が出来たら\nどこへ着て行くのも平気になるって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I can go to the convenience store while wearing the outfit‚\nI'll be fine going anywhere in it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あの衣装を着てコンビニに行ったんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did you actually go to the convenience store wearing that outfit!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "行ってないわよ！？\nそう言われただけで、寮の外には出てないから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't go!\nJust because you said that‚ I haven't even stepped outside the dormitory!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それを聞いて安心しました。でも普段着にするのは\nやめて下さい。破れたりしたら大変ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm relieved to hear that. But please don't make it your everyday wear.\nIt would be troublesome if it gets torn or damaged.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "はーい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それから、こころの言うことは真に受けないで下さい\nそれで愛がいつも大変な目に遭ってるんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ don't take Kokoro's words too seriously.\nAi is always going through a tough time because of that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_04_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなのね。分かったわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see. I understand…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
